      "finding": "The numerical match itself (95.113 MeV vs 95.132 MeV) is presented accurately with proper error propagation. The error budget decomposition is thorough and transparent.",
      "severity": "MINOR",
      "justification": "This is actually a strength of the manuscript - careful error analysis and transparency about uncertainties."
    }
  ]
}
```

